Всем привет. Вакансия от коллег из соседней команды.

*Название вакансии:* Machine learning research engineer
*Офис:* г. Москва, м. Шаболовская
*Описание вакансии и требования к кандидатам:*

IPONWEB is looking for a developer with an interest in machine learning to join us in:
• experimental research of machine learning algorithms in the field of programmatic marketing;
• implementation of these algorithms and surrounding infrastructure for production environments.

You will be dealing with:
• an assortment of optimization problems for various agents in programmatic marketing systems (RTB auctions);
• datasets typically containing millions of events per day (and more);
• various algorithmic challenges in the field of machine learning: feature engineering and selection, hyperparameter optimization, exploitation vs. exploration and bias vs. noise tradeoffs and much more;
• systems which aim to continuously apply these algorithms in a robust, scalable and adaptable fashion;
• short- and long-term financial effect as the ultimate measure of any algorithms efficiency.

Our ideal candidate is:
• experienced in designing and implementing computational and data processing algorithms (especially in machine learning);
• experienced in adapting and tuning machine learning algorithms for a specific problem;
• strong knowledge of C++ and/or Python;
• familiar with basic calculus, probability theory and machine learning theory.

